  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK342">
<l>vēṇṭi ṉuṇṭākat tuṟakka tuṟantapi</l>
<l>ṉīṇṭiyaṟ pāla pala</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>After a man has renounced (all things), there will still be many things in this world (which he may enjoy); if he should desire them, let him, while it is time abandon (the world).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
